	<hr noshade width='80%' align='left' color='#cccccc'><br>Has anyone fought the Bulwarks in CS to see if their gem drop rate is higher than average?<br>
<br>
Here's a comment from someone else:<br>
"Goto Cobalt Scar. <br>
<br>
Down by the Othmir, set up camp on the beach facing the tower where you zone out.. Have someone pull the Bulwarks from under the tower (they are underwater) up on the shore and kill them. <br>
<br>
A) They are good experience <br>
<br>
B) Me and my group have NEVER killed anything that dropped so many spells and quest gems. We were loaded with them by the end of the night."<br>
<br>
Forthyr<BR><BR></td>
